data.title: coin, 1 franc, Algeria (France)
data.meta_description: An Algerian 1 franc coin, circular, the obverse features a left-facing portrait of Liberty within wreath encircled by legend "REPUBLIQUE FRANCAIS", the reverse features the denomination "1 FR" in centre encircled by legend "CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE DE BONE".
data.text:
We have over a million object records online, and we are adding to this all the time. Our records are never finished.
